    public interface AHRegionModel
extends com.liferay.portal.model.BaseModel<AHRegion>
    The base model interface for the AHRegion service. Represents a row in the "AHREGION" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    This interface and its corresponding implementation AHRegionModelImpl exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in AHRegionImpl.
